How it works:
it creates virtual joystick in server and in the local network, send fifa controll of client to the server which can be mapped according to Server's Fifa joystick Controlls.
Needed:
VJOY virtual joystick Driver
(Optional) Screen Duplication on Other PC ..Like MaxiVista TeamViewer etc....


Steps:
1)Server:
-Add ip into textbox 
-MakeServer
-RunFifa
-tell friend to connect on ur ip.
2)Client:
-Add Server ip in the textbox
-Set ur Control in the second tab
-connect and enjoy.